19225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"448fa624d55d498be6fa6b881f9a1c1bc92ef332","tid":989544,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講yerin同有丁係老死🤔</blockquote><br />\n即係邊個呀 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:24:02.000Z","msg":"磪有情囉😊"},{"pid":"7acac27ee2babbf72216bb63bf6eb4233fe19aa6","tid":989544,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:08:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喂<ins>吖咦吔</ins>囉你地記唔記得唧 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁快就三年，最初g持佢依個討論區仲未出現囉 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32999f103de9b48df28b261da179f44969523e60","tid":989544,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽講yerin同有丁係老死🤔</blockquote><br />\n即係邊個呀 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>磪有情囉😊</blockquote><br />\n哦原來佢，叫佢丁就真係唔識未聽過嘛 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜唔係joy先最老友咩 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/24/014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F24%2F014534_12dce3cb521d639bb955ddb0f91a02e5.png&h=feefedce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5955a3bd7f4fe26fabf1e2c0c7bd4df6da5cd1cc","tid":989544,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739061f705f2354eab1c8660fb60fec8a2cc35bf","tid":989544,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"我和yerin18+"},{"pid":"7488d8a09b77b6a84783c8e38bf3e12d8f31f83a","tid":989544,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"初識yerin以為佢有過度活躍 原來呢d叫natural high"},{"pid":"341e8085a3157f1af060d6e946e83c999b8ca102","tid":989544,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6564a2c19d9c575b26789293cdc21bf700970a46","tid":989544,"uid":14208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0f7035f8f53c525b24b267be6e599730864517","tid":989544,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor